OL,3,CDisappointment for many after record
OL,4,Capplications for double TCS London
OL,5,CMarathon
OL,7,FA record number of people applied for
OL,8,Fa place in next year's TCS London
OL,9,FMarathon which will take place across
OL,10,Ftwo days, allowing 100,000 people to
OL,11,Fparticipate.
OL,13,FThere were 1,338,544 ballot
OL,14,Fapplications from the UK and around
OL,15,Fthe world requesting a place in the
OL,16,Fone-off double event which will take
OL,17,Fplace on Saturday April 24 and Sunday
OL,18,FApril 25 2027.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
