OL,3,CDisappointment for many after record
OL,4,Capplications for double TCS London
OL,5,CMarathon
OL,7,FIt was a rise of more than 200,000
OL,8,Fapplications (18%) on the 1,133,813
OL,9,Fwho asked for a ballot place in 2026
OL,10,Fand many were left disappointed when
OL,11,Fresults were sent out on Thursday.
OL,13,FHugh Brasher, chief executive of
OL,14,FLondon Marathon Events which organises
OL,15,Fthe TCS London Marathon, said: "The
OL,16,F2027 Double TCS London Marathon will
OL,17,Fbe a weekend of celebration like no
OL,18,Fother in history.
OL,26,@wD@`OU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
