OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783774107
OL,3,CDisappointment for many after record
OL,4,Capplications for double TCS London
OL,5,CMarathon
OL,7,F"For those who didn't get a place in
OL,8,Fthe ballot, you can still be part of
OL,9,Fthe TCS London Marathon by applying
OL,10,Ffor one of the charity places ` which,
OL,11,Ffor 2027 only, includes the chance to
OL,12,Frun on the Saturday.
OL,14,F"We are thrilled to be able to offer
OL,15,Fthis unique opportunity to take part
OL,16,Facross two days and we can't wait to
OL,17,Fwelcome 100,000 people to the streets
OL,18,Fof London next spring."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOUzD@WO]
