OL,3,CDisappointment for many after record
OL,4,Capplications for double TCS London
OL,5,CMarathon
OL,7,FThe National Autistic Society is the
OL,8,Fofficial charity partner for the TCS
OL,9,FLondon Marathon in 2027.
OL,11,FOn Thursday, Marie Curie said it
OL,12,Fraised more than #2.3 million as the
OL,13,Fmarathon's charity of the year for
OL,14,F2026, five times the #450,000 total
OL,15,Ffrom 2025.
OL,17,FThe sum exceeded the charity's 2026
OL,18,Ffundraising goal to raise #2 million `
OL,19,Fdriven by the 744 people who ran for
OL,20,FMarie Curie and the generosity of
OL,21,Fsupporters.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
