CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F377A1783774107
OL,3,CDisappointment for many after record
OL,4,Capplications for double TCS London
OL,5,CMarathon
OL,7,FThe #2.3 million raised was the
OL,8,Fequivalent of 100,000 hours of nursing
OL,9,Fcare or enough to fund the support
OL,10,Fline for more than six years, the
OL,11,Fcharity said.
OL,13,FChief executive Matthew Reed said
OL,14,Fbeing charity of the year was "a huge
OL,15,Fhonour", adding: "We're so grateful to
OL,16,Fall our runners and supporters for
OL,17,Fhelping us raise this remarkable sum
OL,18,Fof money.
OL,26,@vD@_OUwD@GO]wD@ROU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
